serious? - Mm-hmm.

34:23.542 --> 34:25.868
- You really want to do it?
- Yeah.

34:27.197 --> 34:29.118
Yeah. I do. I really do.

34:33.239 --> 34:34.190
Yeah, it sounds crazy,

34:34.216 --> 34:36.846
but... but nice.

34:44.893 --> 34:46.541
Look at us, Mother.

34:47.385 --> 34:50.570
We are very charming people.

34:50.922 --> 34:52.145
[both laughing]

34:52.583 --> 34:54.960
The hospitality business on the islands

34:54.985 --> 34:56.105
